name: Moonie
description:
Unique face cloth made from natural, un-bleached muslin. 
Contrast Moonie Label
Handmade in the UK
Double layered
Three Moonie's per pack
FREE handmade 'Neil' toy!

The natural muslin fabric helps to gently exfoliate the skin and buff away impurites leaving the skin naturally glowing. Moonie's can be used an daily essential or a weekly treat!
Suitable for all skin types.

name: Neil
description:
